title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Veering away from a customary practice today reveals a solution to a problem you didnt even know existed. However, you might be emotionally unsatisfied unless you venture far enough into uncharted territory because the flamboyant Leo Moon doesnt suffer boredom well. Thread together new elements in a creative manner. For instance, a complex project inspires you to create a better filing system or a detour on your commute to work directs you to another path that pares down your travel time.
